      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "ro. Tad brehze Israëta Behr-\nni us to KUNGU / un fazzija:\nWehs effam prett tew grehkojjschi /\njo mehs effam muhsfu Deewu at-\nstahjuschi / un teem Baalim kal-\npojfschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Bet tas KUNGS fazzt-\nja us Israëta Behrneem: Woj\nes juhs ne efmu tspestijs no teem\nEgiptexeem / un no teem Amori-\ntexeem / un no Ammona Behr-\nneem/ un no teem Wihlistexeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Un Zihdonexeem/un Ama-\nlekitexeem / un Maonitexeem/ kas\njuhs spaidtja / kad juhs us man\nbrehzat/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Tomehr effat juhs mann\natstahjuschi/ un zitteem Deetweem\nkalpojuscht/tadeht es juhs ne grib-\nbu tspestiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Eita un brehzeet us juh-\nseem Deerweem / fo juhs effat ts-\nmeklejschees / lai tee juhs tspestit\njuhfu Behdu Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Bet Israëta Behrni faz-\nzija us to KUNGU: Mehs effam\ngrehkojuschi / darrf tu mums pehz\nwiſſu / kas tew patihk / tsglahb\nmuhs tikkat scho Brihdt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un tee mette nohſt tohs\nfweschus Deerwus no jewis / un\nkalpoja tam KUNGAM / tad\ntappe wiꞥſam pahr Israëta Beh-\ndahm schehl.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Un Ammona Behrni tap-\npe fataukti / un apmettehs eeksch\nGileadas/ un Israëta Behrni fa-\npulzejahs un apmettehs eeksch\nMitzpas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Tad fazzija tee Eaudis/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tee Wirfneeki no Gileadas we-\nus ohtru : Kas buhs tas Wih-\nkas fahks karroht prett Ammo-\nBehrneem/ tam buhs par Gal-\nbuht pahr wiﬀeem / kas Gile-\ndshwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XI. Nodalla.\nJewtus weens Maukas-Behrns : 1. Tohp\nto kauschu Wirfneeku eezelts : 5/6.\nta Wehsſus pee teem Ammonitereem M-\ndeht: 12. Apfohlahs Dewam ne-ap-\nmigi: 29/30. Usware tohs Eenaideek\n33. Tarrfawu Apfohlichannu fawu wee-\nMeitu nodshdams : 34/39.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. Ewtus tas Gileadite\nbijs weens stiprs Kar-\nWihrs / bet wiꞥſch b-\nweens Maukas-Behrns / toin-\nGileads bij Jewtu dsemdinajs-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Kad nu Gileada See-\nwixaim Behrnus dseindeja /\nſchabs Seewas Behrnt pee-an-\ntad igdsinne tee Jewtu/ un fazz-\nus to : Tew ne buhs eemant-\nimhsfu Tehwa Mamma/ jo tu-\nweenas zittas Seewas Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Tad behdse Jewtus no-\nweem Brabteem / un dsihw-\nToba Semmē/un pee Jewtus\nvutzejahs Watkas-Wihrt / un-\ngahje ar wiꞥſu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Un pehz kahdahm Deena-\ncarroja Ammona Behrni pr-\nIsraëlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Un kad Ammona Beh-\nprett Israëlu karreja/tad tee-\nzajee no Gileadas nogahje /\ndabbuja Jewtu no Toba Sei-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Un tee fazzija us Jew-\nNahz/ un effi mums par Kar-\nWirfneeku / un karro prett A-\nmona Behrneem.\n"
    }
  ],
